window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Every hero has a beginning. So does every villain.</p> <p>Titan, the world’s greatest superhero, has been murdered by his longtime archenemy Lord Borealis. And from the ashes rises a new generation.</p> <p>Gifted with powers on the night of Titan’s death, 15-year-old Hugo awakes to the strange world of superheroes. A world he isn’t prepared for.</p> <p>But with godlike powers and a history of tragedy, will Hugo become a guardian of justice...or agent of chaos?</p> <p>Warning: Contains moderate swearing and big damn superhero action. If you’re not a fan of moderate swearing or big damn superhero action, this book might not be for you.</p>"; 
